    "Tailoring the model to recognize domain-specific product names can lead to heightened accuracy and relevance in recommendations.To further refine our approach, advanced data preprocessing techniques warrant exploration.",
    "This includes strategies for handling misspelled words and text that departs from standard grammar and syntax, ensuring the model's robustness in the face of diverse textual idiosyncrasies.",
